docs.abstract: The personal information of customers at its Starwood hotels, including names, dates of birth, passport numbers and payment numbers could be at risk, the chain said.
docs.snippet: The personal information of customers at its Starwood hotels, including names, dates of birth, passport numbers and payment numbers could be at risk, the chain said.
docs.lead_paragraph: The hotel chain asked guests checking in for a treasure trove of personal information: credit cards, addresses and sometimes passport numbers. On Friday, consumers learned the risk. Marriott International revealed that hackers had breached its Starwood reservation system and had stolen the personal data of up to 500 million guests.

headline.main: Marriott Hacking Exposes Data of Up to 500 Million Guests
headline.print_headline: Marriott Breach Puts Data of 500 Million at Risk

docs.abstract: Workers in the company’s offices around the world protested how it has handled cases of sexual harassment and misconduct.
docs.snippet: Workers in the company’s offices around the world protested how it has handled cases of sexual harassment and misconduct.
docs.lead_paragraph: In New York, more than 3,000 gathered in a city park and carried signs that said, “O.K. Google, really?” In Dublin, dozens filled a sidewalk. And in Silicon Valley, thousands poured out of office buildings into a common outdoor area and chanted: “Stand up! Fight back!”

headline.main: Google Walkout: Employees Stage Protest Over Handling of Sexual Harassment
headline.print_headline: Google Workers Worldwide Walk Out Over Handling of Harassment

docs.abstract: Eager candidates offered name changes, helipads and even cactuses to entice the company into setting up shop.
docs.snippet: Eager candidates offered name changes, helipads and even cactuses to entice the company into setting up shop.
docs.lead_paragraph: After 14 months of pitches, meetings and offers of incentives and name changes, Amazon announced on Tuesday that its second headquarters would be on two sites: one in Long Island City, Queens, and another in Arlington, Va. The company is also developing a smaller operations and logistics facility in Nashville.

headline.main: Amazon HQ2: How New York and Virginia Won the Beauty Contest
